column1: #cell_viability_marker : marker used to detect cell viability in flow cytometery
#MOI : (viral_integration/cell) multiplicity of infection of lentivirus transfected into donor T-cells to create CART effectors
#standard_cell_concentration : (cells/mL) concentration of cells from serially-diluted non-transduced donor cells counted with Vi-CELL
#id_effector : CAR pCDL plasmid id expressed by effector cells
